Question: The left image includes at least one black fish with white dots swimming above pale anemone tendrils, and the right image features at least one orange-and-white clownfish above pale anemone tendrils.

Reference Answer: False

Right image URL: https://images.robertharding.com/preview/RM/RH/HORIZONTAL/1159-286.jpg

Original program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Does the image include at least one black fish with white dots swimming above pale anemone tendrils?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Does the image feature at least one orange-and-white clownfish above pale anemone tendrils?')
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} or {ANSWER1}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
